Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.95,0:00:30.30,op_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}堅信未來 若在前方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:36.08,op_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}倘為戰鬥 不惜此身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.31,0:00:43.17,op_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}信念交織 斷不動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.36,0:00:49.17,op_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}此番誓言 深信不疑
